---
description: Package dependency direction and server/client boundary rules for the hypha-web monorepo
alwaysApply: true
---

## Package dependency direction

```
apps/web → epics → core → storage-postgres
         → ui
         → authentication → evm
         → i18n
         → feature-flags
         → notifications → core
         → chat-server → core
```

Never reverse this direction. Circular deps are a build failure.

## Server / client boundary

- Server-only code: `'use server'` directive, or imported from a `./server` export path (e.g. `@hypha-platform/core/server`)
- Client-only code: `'use client'` directive, or `@hypha-platform/core/client`
- Never import `./server` paths from a client component

## Database injection

Always pass `db` as a config argument: `queryFn({ db })`. Never import `db` directly inside query/mutation functions.
